ation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/4d4d9a872a55b209f2eb7cc23a71e5e1541bd1f4" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.671ex; width:2.985ex; height:2.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle H_{=
1}}"></span>) is true. It is commonly denoted by <span class=3D"mwe-math-el=
ement mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-ma=
th-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1=
